==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Straightness
<hw>Straight"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality, condition, or
state, of being straight; <as>as, the <ex>straightness</ex> of a
path</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Straightness</ent>⟦br⟧

